title: my phone is dead and it keeps making a vibration sound and high pitched noise
content: basically a few weeks ago i dropped my phone and cracked it very small crack, then i dropped it in my bath the other day left it in a bowl of rice all the condensation gone out of the cameras but now i have turned it on and well on my PC it says Qualcomm HS-USB QDLoader 9008 as the device, however it constantly makes a high pitched buzz and vibrates periodically i would like to know why this is happening.
